**Professional Profile**
Lê Tự Huy is an emerging professional in the Information Technology sector, demonstrating capabilities as both a Software Engineer and Web Developer. As a Software Engineer, they were responsible for developing a high-performance Chinese dictionary application, optimizing MySQL queries, implementing fast data retrieval, and integrating AI for character recognition. In their Web Developer capacity, they designed responsive UI/UX for an e-commerce website, developed core features including search, filtering, and login, and optimized database architecture with SQL queries.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Their technical expertise spans Python, HTML, CSS, PHP, SQL Server, MySQL, and Laravel. Lê Tự Huy also possesses strong skills in UI/UX Design, Responsive Design, AI Integration, Data Analysis, and System Architecture Optimization.

**Education & Certifications**
Lê Tự Huy holds a Bachelor of Computer Science from Tôn Đức Thắng University. Complementing their academic background, they have achieved an APTIS (B2) certification, indicating a solid command of English.